libc++ runtime package @LLVM_VERSION@

Target triple: @TARGET_TRIPLE@
Target kind: @TARGET_KIND@

Included runtime families:
  compiler-rt builtins and runtime libraries
  libunwind
  libc++abi
  libc++

This package intentionally contains runtime headers and libraries only. It does
not contain the full LLVM SDK, clang, lld, or clang-tools-extra.

Unlike general SDK dependency packages, this runtime package preserves both
shared libraries and static runtime archives such as libc++.a, libc++abi.a,
libunwind.a, and compiler-rt archives.
